Class FreeCellTestDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • FreeCellTestDriver

  • public class FreeCellTestDriver
extends java.lang.Object
    Driver class to test all methods of FreeCell. This will not be testing the Game Model, Game Rules GUI, Table GUI, Welcome GUI, Value (enum) or Suit (enum) classes.

    Mikael Hinton & Brian Belcher
